==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Salaam
<hw>Sa*laam"</hw> <pr>(s⟦adot⟧*l⟦aum⟧m")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Same as <er>Salam</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Finally, Josiah might have made his <qex>salaam</qex> to the
exciseman just as he was folding up that letter.</q> <rj><qau>Prof.
Wilson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

