==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Salaam
<hw>Sa*laam"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To make or perform a
salam.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I have <qex>salaamed</qex> and kowtowed to him.</q> <rj><qau>H.
James.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Salability</ent>⟦br⟧
